            "title": "Mabhora muBhokisi",
            "created_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2026-02-04T08:26:25+01:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003EWed, 02/04/2026 - 08:26\u003C/time\u003E\n",
            "updated_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2026-02-10T06:24:47+01:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003ETue, 02/10/2026 - 06:24\u003C/time\u003E\n",
            "summary": "Zvokushandisa Zvaunoda: Mabhora mashoma akasiyana kukura (aya anogona kunge ari mabhora akapfava awakagadzira kubva mumasokisi akapetwa kana pepanhau); makadhibhokisi makuru kupfuura bhora guru.",
            "body": "\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EZvokushandisa Zvaunoda:\u003C/strong\u003E Mabhora mashoma akasiyana kukura (aya anogona kunge ari mabhora akapfava awakagadzira kubva mumasokisi akapetwa kana pepanhau); makadhibhokisi makuru kupfuura bhora guru.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EZvamunogona Kuita Pamwe Chete:\u003C/strong\u003E Gadzira mutambo wemumba (kana mabhora akapfava) kana kunze. Kokai mwana wenyu kuti aedze kukanda bhora mubhokisi. Tangai nekuratidza mwana wenyu maitirwo acho, uye pakutanga mirai pedyo nebhokisi. Sezvo mwana wako achiwedzera kugona kukanda, mukurudzire kuti adzokere kumashure zvishoma nezvishoma achiedza kukanda ari kure. Edzai izvi nemabhora akasiyana kukura. Mwana wenyu achafarirawo kuita izvi ari ega. Kana mwana wenyu achifarira, unogona zvakare kuverenga kuti kangani kaanogona kuwana mabhora mubhokisi.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EZviri Kudzidzwa Nomwana Wenyu:\u003C/strong\u003E Mwana wenyu ari kudzidza unyanzvi hwake hwomuviri mune iyi nemimwe mitambo. Mwana wenyu ari kudzidza kudzora mafambiro ake uye kukanda nomazvo. Kuwedzera kugona unyanzvi uhu kunobatsira kusimudzira kuzvivimba kwemwana wako. Kana ukawedzera kuverenga pamutambo uyu, mwana wako achavandudzawo hunyanzvi hwake hwekutanga hwemasvomhu.\u003C/p\u003E",
            "activity_category": 721,
            "equipment": 0,
