            "title": "Kutaura pamberi pegirazi",
            "created_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2026-01-26T09:39:54+01:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003EMon, 01/26/2026 - 09:39\u003C/time\u003E\n",
            "updated_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2026-02-10T06:24:47+01:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003ETue, 02/10/2026 - 06:24\u003C/time\u003E\n",
            "summary": "Zvokushandisa Zvaunoda: Girazi.Zvamunogona Kuita Pamwe Chete: Kokai mudiki wenyu kuti atarise mugirazi. Mirai pamberi pegirazi, imi vaviri pamwe chete. Tangai nekukwazisa uye kudzokorora mazwi kumwana wenyu.Anotanga nokutaura mazwi akasiyana-siyana ekuseka, mhuka, zvinhu. Mirira mhinduro yake. Pakutanga, anoshamisika, asi nekuramba achiita, mudiki wenyu anotangawo kuita ruzha.Dzokororai ruzha runoitwa nemwana wenyu.",
            "body": "\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EZvokushandisa Zvaunoda:\u003C/strong\u003E Girazi.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EZvamunogona Kuita Pamwe Chete:\u003C/strong\u003E Kokai mudiki wenyu kuti atarise mugirazi. Mirai pamberi pegirazi, imi vaviri pamwe chete. Tangai nekukwazisa uye kudzokorora mazwi kumwana wenyu.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EAnotanga nokutaura mazwi akasiyana-siyana ekuseka, mhuka, zvinhu. Mirira mhinduro yake. Pakutanga, anoshamisika, asi nekuramba achiita, mudiki wenyu anotangawo kuita ruzha.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EDzokororai ruzha runoitwa nemwana wenyu.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EZviri Kudzidza Mwana Wenyu:\u003C/strong\u003E Chiitiko ichi chiri nyore chichabvumira mwana wenyu kuti azvizive uye azvitaurire mumutauro uye kuti azokwanisa kuzviziva munguva inotevera mune vamwe vanhu.\u003C/p\u003E",
