            "created_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2026-01-22T14:08:18+01:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003EThu, 01/22/2026 - 14:08\u003C/time\u003E\n",
            "updated_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2026-02-10T06:24:47+01:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003ETue, 02/10/2026 - 06:24\u003C/time\u003E\n",
            "summary": "Zvishandiso Zvaunoda: Girazi.Zvamunogona Kuita Pamwe Chete: Panguva yechiitiko ichi, mudiki wenyu achadzidza kuzviziva nekuzviona akatarisa mugirazi.Pachiitiko ichi, garai pedyo nemwana wenyu kuitira kuti utaure mazwi akadai sekuti \"mudiki uyu ndiwe\", \"amai / baba vari pedyo newe\", \"mwana akanaka sei\", \"iyi mhino yako\", \"uyu muromo wako\".Fungai nezvezvimwe zvisimbiso zvinogona kubatsira mudiki wenyu.",
            "body": "\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EZvishandiso Zvaunoda:\u003C/strong\u003E Girazi.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EZvamunogona Kuita Pamwe Chete:\u003C/strong\u003E Panguva yechiitiko ichi, mudiki wenyu achadzidza kuzviziva nekuzviona akatarisa mugirazi.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EPachiitiko ichi, garai pedyo nemwana wenyu kuitira kuti utaure mazwi akadai sekuti \"mudiki uyu ndiwe\", \"amai / baba vari pedyo newe\", \"mwana akanaka sei\", \"iyi mhino yako\", \"uyu muromo wako\".\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EFungai nezvezvimwe zvisimbiso zvinogona kubatsira mudiki wenyu.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EZviri Kudzidza Mwana Wako:\u003C/strong\u003E Zvose izvi zvichabatsira mwana wenyu kuti atange kuziva uye kukudziridza kufamba kwemuviri kuburikidza nekucherechedza uye kukuzivai imi mugirazi.\u003C/p\u003E",
