            "title": "Ukudinga Izinto Ezifihliweyo",
            "created_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2026-02-12T21:11:29+01:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003EThu, 02/12/2026 - 21:11\u003C/time\u003E\n",
            "updated_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2026-02-12T21:52:49+01:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003EThu, 02/12/2026 - 21:52\u003C/time\u003E\n",
            "summary": "Izinto Ozidingayo: Amathoyi ambalwa abuthakathaka kumbe izinto zangekhaya eziphephileyo lezikhangayo emntwaneni.",
            "body": "\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EIzinto Ozidingayo:\u003C/strong\u003E Amathoyi ambalwa abuthakathaka kumbe izinto zangekhaya eziphephileyo lezikhangayo emntwaneni.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EOngakwenza Ndawonye:\u003C/strong\u003E Beka umntwana wakho ngesisu sakhe, ku-\u003Cem\u003Ecarpet,\u003C/em\u003E kumbe kwezinye indawo ezibuthakathaka. Hlala ukuze ubone ubuso bomntwana wakho futhi ulawule ukuphepha kwakhe. Beka amathoyi amanengana ehlangothini olulodwa (kwesokunxele kumbe kwesokudla) lomntwana lapho angafinyeleli khona kodwa endaweni angawabona khona. Lindela ukuthi awabone kumbe umkhange ngelizwi elimangeleyo (uthi: \"Aaaa, siphetheni lapha?\"). Lindela umntwana wakho ukuthi agiqike ukuze afinyelele enye yezinto. Nxa umntwana wakho engazami yedwa, mncedise ukuthi agiqeke esuka esiswini esiya emhlane ukuze akwazi ukufinyelela ezintweni. Mkhuthaze ngelizwi elilomdlandla, ukubobotheka kakhulu. Lapho esekela ukuba lokuthakazelela, ekhangela eceleni kumbe etshengisa ukungathabi - phinda umdlalo ngezinye izinto, ngakolunye uhlangothi.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ELokho Umntwana Wakho Akufundayo:\u003C/strong\u003E Umntwana wakho ulethuba lokuhlola izinto ngokuzikhangela, ukuzisusa esandleni esinye esiya kwesinye, ukuzithinta, lokuzifaka emlonyeni.\u003C/p\u003E",
            "activity_category": 731,
            "equipment": 0,
            "type_of_support": 8731,
