            "type": "Games",
            "title": "Ngiyazibuka Esibukweni",
            "created_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2026-02-12T21:05:08+01:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003EThu, 02/12/2026 - 21:05\u003C/time\u003E\n",
            "updated_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2026-02-19T14:00:01+01:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003EThu, 02/19/2026 - 14:00\u003C/time\u003E\n",
            "summary": "Izinto Ozidingayo: Isibuko.Elingakwenza Ndawonye: Phakathi komdlalo lo, umntwana uzafunda ukuzinanzelela esibukweni.Kulo mdlalo, hlala eduze lomntwana ukuze utsho imitsho efana lale, “lomntwana omncane nguwe”, “umama/ubaba useduze kwakho”, “khangela ukuthi umntwana muhle njani”, “likhala lakho leli”, “lo ngumlomo wakho”.Cabanga amanye amazwi akhuthazayo ongawakhuluma.",
            "body": "\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EIzinto Ozidingayo:\u003C/strong\u003E Isibuko.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EElingakwenza Ndawonye:\u003C/strong\u003E Phakathi komdlalo lo, umntwana uzafunda ukuzinanzelela esibukweni.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EKulo mdlalo, hlala eduze lomntwana ukuze utsho imitsho efana lale, “lomntwana omncane nguwe”, “umama/ubaba useduze kwakho”, “khangela ukuthi umntwana muhle njani”, “likhala lakho leli”, “lo ngumlomo wakho”.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ECabanga amanye amazwi akhuthazayo ongawakhuluma.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EOkufundwa Ngumntwana:\u003C/strong\u003E Konke lokhu kuncedisa umntwana ukuthi aqale ukubona lokuthuthukisa ukunyakaza komzimba ngokukhangela futhi akubone esibukweni.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E \u003C/p\u003E",
