            "updated_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2026-02-20T08:36:05+01:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003EFri, 02/20/2026 - 08:36\u003C/time\u003E\n",
            "summary": "Izinto Ozidingayo: Isibuko.Elingakwenza Ndawonye: Nxusa umntwana ukuthi akhangele esibukweni. Mana laye phambi kwesibuko. Qala ngokubingelela lokuphindaphinda imisindo emntwaneni.Qala ngokwenza imisindo ehlukahlukeneyo yokuhleka, eyenyamazana, eyezinto. Linda impendulo yakhe. Ekuqaleni, uzamangala, kodwa ngokuphindaphindiweyo, umntwana uzaqala ukwenza imisindo.Phinda imisindo eyenziwa ngumntwana.",
            "body": "\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EIzinto Ozidingayo:\u003C/strong\u003E Isibuko.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EElingakwenza Ndawonye:\u003C/strong\u003E Nxusa umntwana ukuthi akhangele esibukweni. Mana laye phambi kwesibuko. Qala ngokubingelela lokuphindaphinda imisindo emntwaneni.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EQala ngokwenza imisindo ehlukahlukeneyo yokuhleka, eyenyamazana, eyezinto. Linda impendulo yakhe. Ekuqaleni, uzamangala, kodwa ngokuphindaphindiweyo, umntwana uzaqala ukwenza imisindo.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EPhinda imisindo eyenziwa ngumntwana.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EOkufundwa Ngumntwana :\u003C/strong\u003E Lo mdlalo olula uzavumela umntwana ukuthi ananzelele njalo aveze imizwa yakhe ngokukhuluma njalo ayenelise ukuyinanzelela kwabanye abantu ngokuhamba kwesikhathi.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E \u003C/p\u003E",
