            "title": "Ukunika i-massage",
            "created_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2026-02-12T20:30:26+01:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003EThu, 02/12/2026 - 20:30\u003C/time\u003E\n",
            "updated_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2026-02-12T20:43:36+01:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003EThu, 02/12/2026 - 20:43\u003C/time\u003E\n",
            "summary": "Izinto Ozidingayo: Azikho; ungasebenzisa amafutha nxa ufuna.  Elingakwenza Ndawonye: Sizaqala enyaweni siye ekhanda. Ungaqala ngokuhlikihla izandla zakho ndawonye ukuze uzikhudumeze. Ungasebenzisa amafutha okugcoba nxa ufuna. Lalisa umntwana endaweni eyisicaba, ebuthakathaka ukuze akhululeke.",
            "body": "\u003Cp\u003EIzinto Ozidingayo: Azikho; ungasebenzisa \u003Cem\u003Eamafutha nxa ufuna.  \u003C/em\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EElingakwenza Ndawonye:\u003C/strong\u003E Sizaqala enyaweni siye ekhanda. Ungaqala ngokuhlikihla izandla zakho ndawonye ukuze uzikhudumeze. Ungasebenzisa amafutha okugcoba nxa ufuna. Lalisa umntwana endaweni eyisicaba, ebuthakathaka ukuze akhululeke.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EInyawo:\u003C/strong\u003E Thatha olunye unyawo lomntwana ulukhangelise kwesokudla lesokunxele, uphinde ulukhangelise kwesokunxele usiya kwesokudla, kuphindaphinde lokhu okwezikhathi ezimbalwa. Bese usenza i-\u003Cem\u003Emassage \u003C/em\u003Eenyaweni lomntwana kusukela enqagaleni usiya emazwaneni. Tshintsha unyawo uphinde njalo. \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EIzithende:\u003C/strong\u003E Sebenzisa izithupha zakho ukwenza izigombolozi ezithendeni zonyawo lomntwana. Tshintsha unyawo bese uphinda.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EAmazwane:\u003C/strong\u003E Ukuze uqedelele inyawo, bamba inyawo zomntwana phakathi kwesithupha sakho lomunwe wokukhomba ubusudonsa kancane amazwane omntwana kuze kube yilapho iminwe wakho itshelela emazwaneni omntwana. Yenza lokhu ngamazwane wonke ngalinye ngalinye.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ELokho Umntwana Akufundayo:\u003C/strong\u003E Ukunika i-\u003Cem\u003Emassage\u003C/em\u003E kunganikeza inzuzo ezihlukeneyo zempilo. Njengesibonelo, i-\u003Cem\u003Emassage \u003C/em\u003Eemntwaneni ingasiza ekwandiseni ukuxhumana phakathi komntwana lomama/lobaba futhi kusize umntwana ukuba akhululeke ngokunciphisa ukukhala lokunciphisa ama-\u003Cem\u003Estress\u003C/em\u003E \u003Cem\u003Ehormones\u003C/em\u003E.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E \u003C/p\u003E",
            "activity_category": 721,
            "equipment": 0,
