            "title": "Ukudobha Idoti",
            "created_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2026-02-12T20:13:13+01:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003EThu, 02/12/2026 - 20:13\u003C/time\u003E\n",
            "updated_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2026-02-12T20:15:16+01:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003EThu, 02/12/2026 - 20:15\u003C/time\u003E\n",
            "summary": "Izinto Ozidingayo: Ama-gloves; Isikhwama se-bin; okokudobhisa idoti (ungakhetha ukuba lakho lokhu).",
            "body": "\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EIzinto Ozidingayo:\u003C/strong\u003E Ama-\u003Cem\u003Egloves\u003C/em\u003E; Isikhwama se-bin; okokudobhisa idoti (\u003Cem\u003Eungakhetha ukuba lakho lokhu\u003C/em\u003E).\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EElingakwenza Ndawonye:\u003C/strong\u003E Phuma lomntwana/labantwana bakho liye endaweni engcoliswe ngedoti -- kungaba yindawo yesikolo sabo, kumbe indawo yokudlala, kumbe ipaki yomphakathi yangakini. Ngemva kokuqiniseka ukuthi akukho okuyingozi kumbe okulimazayo, gqoka ama-gloves ubusuqala ukudobha! Yenza umntwana wakho ukuthi ananzelele inyamazana zeganga, ukuze akwazi ukubona ukuthi zonke inyamazana lezibungu sezilekhaya eliphephileyo lelihlanzekileyo ngenxa yomsebenzi wakhe. \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EYenza umfanekiso kumbe i-model ngedoti yasendlini yakho usebenzisa izinto ezifana lamaphakethe okudla, amagabha, amagabha lamaphepha alahlwayo.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ELokho Umntwana Wakho Akufundayo:\u003C/strong\u003E Lapho liphumele phandle, lizabona idoti endaweni yonke. Ukudobha idoti kulithuba elihle lokufunda, ngakho-ke kungani uthathi uhambo lomntwana wakho futhi umtshengise ukuthi lesi senzo esilula singasiza kanjani ekugcineni indawo yokuhlala yenyamazana zeganga ukuze ziphile kuhle. Lokhu kunakekela imvelo kuzophinda kubenze bananzelele ukuthi umuntu oyedwa angenza umehluko omkhulu!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E \u003C/p\u003E",
            "activity_category": 726,
            "equipment": 0,
            "type_of_support": 8731,
            "child_age": [696],
