            "created_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2026-02-12T19:32:52+01:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003EThu, 02/12/2026 - 19:32\u003C/time\u003E\n",
            "updated_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2026-02-12T19:36:52+01:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003EThu, 02/12/2026 - 19:36\u003C/time\u003E\n",
            "summary": "Izinto Ozidingayo: Amathoyi ale-size ehlukeneyo kanye lendlela yokwenziwa kumbe ingubo ebuthakathaka.Elingakwenza Ndawonye: Ngaphambi kokuthi uqale, qiniseka ukuthi uyayilungisa indawo. Ungabeka umntwana wakho endaweni ekhululekileyo, phambi kwakho, ekhaphethini, embhedeni kumbe esihlalweni.",
            "body": "\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EIzinto Ozidingayo:\u003C/strong\u003E Amathoyi ale-size ehlukeneyo kanye lendlela yokwenziwa kumbe ingubo ebuthakathaka.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EElingakwenza Ndawonye:\u003C/strong\u003E Ngaphambi kokuthi uqale, qiniseka ukuthi uyayilungisa indawo. Ungabeka umntwana wakho endaweni ekhululekileyo, phambi kwakho, ekhaphethini, embhedeni kumbe esihlalweni.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EUkuze uqale lo msebenzi, ungalungisa izandla zomntwana wakho ngokwenza i-\u003Cem\u003Emassage\u003C/em\u003E encane ukuze akwazi ukuphendula i-\u003Cem\u003Estimulation\u003C/em\u003E omnika yona. Khona-ke ungakwazi ukunikeza umntwana wakho ithoyi ukuze alizwe, ubusulibeka khatshana ukuze azame ukulifinyelela.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ENxa ungelayo ithoyi, ungasebenzisa ingubo ebuthakathaka ukuze umntwana wakho azame ukuyifinyelela ikude. Khumbula ukujabulela lokuthakazelela impumelelo yakhe.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ELokho Umntwana Wakho Akufundayo:\u003C/strong\u003E Ngalo msebenzi, uzancedisa umntwana wakho omncane ukuthi afinyelele izinto ngesandla esisodwa ngokusebenzisa ukuxhumana kwesandla lelihlo.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E \u003C/p\u003E",
            "activity_category": 721,
